com.hexaware.entity

Class Incidents

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hexaware.entity.Incidents

  • public class Incidents
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an incident in the system.

    An instance of this class contains information about an incident, including its ID, type, date, location (latitude and longitude), description, status, victim ID, and suspect ID.
